Description: Incident-first root-cause analysis console for Linux
 v0.41.2 fixes two fleet-mode bugs: the embedded web dashboard no longer
 returns 401 on /v1/hosts and /v1/incidents (hub now sets a cookie on the
 HTML page and accepts either cookie or header on read endpoints); and
 xtop --daemon --fleet-hub ... actually pushes to the hub now (previously
 the daemon path skipped fleet-client initialization).
